caption:
As summer comes to a close, we wanted to share our favorite #StayOutThere moments you tagged us in this season:

👟 @cotezi hiked 800+ miles across the Hayduke Trail in Olympus & Lone Peak​

👟 @gracemumm conquered the PCT for the second year in a row wearing Olympus 6​

👟 @gabere is training for his first 100 miler in Mont Blanc Carbon ​

👟 @juliana.marieee got married in her Lone Peaks

👟 @marco.leipold roadtripped with his Torin 7​

👟 @brianadesanctis completed her thru-hike and became the first woman to solo thru-hike the ADT (she wore 27 pairs of Lone Peak!)​

👟 @abbycazam hiked the Kumano Kodo wearing Lone Peak ​

#AltraRunning #StayOutThere​
